rows.label: qst104208_msg0001
rows.name:
I wonder if we can really build
a whole school by ourselves...

rows.label: qst104208_msg0101
rows.name:
I was told any kind of ore is
fine. Did you bring some?

rows.label: qst104208_msg0121
rows.name:
I don't think we have enough to
meet Hummer-san's request... Can
we really build a school?

rows.label: qst104208_msg0141
rows.name:
We've gathered the amount
Hummer-san asked for! Thank you!

rows.label: qst104208_msg0161
rows.name:
When the materials are all here,
it gets kind of exciting! I'll do
my best to build the school!

rows.label: qst104208_msg0201
rows.name:
He said he's going to crush
all the ore into powder and
then harden it again.
